==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Novenary
<hw>Nov"e*na*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>novenarius</ets>, from <ets>novem</ets> nine.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to the number nine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Novenary</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Novenary
<hw>Nov"e*na*ry</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The number of nine units; nine,
collectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Novene</ent>⟦br⟧
